\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {5.4}{\ignorespaces The equivalent electric and magnetic dipole moments of the monopole antenna. To enable direct comparison with the magnetic dipole moment, the electric dipole moment is weighted with the free space impedance $\eta _0$ (see \cref {sec:prep_dip}).}}{49}{figure.caption.32}%
